
To install ShowMeTheShell you should do:

mkdir showmetheshell
cd showmetheshell/
git clone http://github.com/vti/showmetheshell.git .
git submodule init
git submodule update
sudo cpan -i IO::Pty
sudo cpan -i Term::VT102
perl showmetheshell

After that the system will be avaliable at http://localhost:3000

The login and password you can find in the beginnig of the file "showmetheshell".

